    "1 cup powdered sugar",
    "1 tsp vanilla extract",
    "1 tbsp honey",
    "1 tsp ground up lavender",
    "1-2 tbsp milk",
    "1| Heat up milk in microwave for 30 seconds. Add in lavender. Let steep for 10 minutes. Strain.",
    "2| Whisk in sugar, extract, honey."
